### ============================================================================
### OrderService - API Tests
###
### Fluxo recomendado:
### 1. Register User
### 2. Login
### 3. Copiar token retornado para variável @token
### 4. Create Order
### 5. Copiar id retornado para variável @orderId
### 6. Confirm Order
### 7. Get Order
### 8. Cancel Order
### ============================================================================

@host = http://localhost:8080

### ============================================================================
### AUTH VARIABLES
### ============================================================================

@username = admin
@password = admin

### Token JWT obtido no endpoint /auth/token
@token =

### ============================================================================
### ORDER VARIABLES
### ============================================================================

### Atualize após criar um pedido
@orderId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Produtos seedados automaticamente pela aplicação
@product1 = 1
@product2 = 4

### ============================================================================
### AUTH - REGISTER
### ============================================================================

### Cria um novo usuário
POST {{host}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### ============================================================================
### AUTH - LOGIN
### ============================================================================

### Retorna um JWT
POST {{host}}/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### ============================================================================
### ORDERS - CREATE
### ============================================================================

### Cria um pedido válido
POST {{host}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "currency": "BRL",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": {{product1}},
      "quantity": 2
    },
    {
      "productId": {{product2}},
      "quantity": 4
    }
  ]
}

### ============================================================================
### ORDERS - CREATE (EMPTY ITEMS)
### Deve retornar 400
### ============================================================================

POST {{host}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "currency": "BRL",
  "items": []
}

### ============================================================================
### ORDERS - CREATE (PRODUCT NOT FOUND)
### Deve retornar 404
### ============================================================================

POST {{host}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "currency": "BRL",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 9999,
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}

### ============================================================================
### ORDERS - CREATE (INSUFFICIENT STOCK)
### Deve retornar 409
### ============================================================================

POST {{host}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "currency": "BRL",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": {{product1}},
      "quantity": 999999
    }
  ]
}

### ============================================================================
### ORDERS - GET BY ID
### ============================================================================

GET {{host}}/orders/{{orderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================================================
### ORDERS - GET BY ID (NOT FOUND)
### Deve retornar 404
### ============================================================================

GET {{host}}/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================================================
### ORDERS - GET ALL
### ============================================================================

GET {{host}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================================================
### ORDERS - GET ALL (PAGED)
### ============================================================================

GET {{host}}/orders?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================================================
### ORDERS - GET ALL (DATE FILTER)
### ============================================================================

GET {{host}}/orders?page=1&pageSize=10&from=2025-01-01&to=2025-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================================================
### ORDERS - CONFIRM
### ============================================================================

POST {{host}}/orders/{{orderId}}/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================================================
### ORDERS - CONFIRM (NOT FOUND)
### Deve retornar 404
### ============================================================================

POST {{host}}/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================================================
### ORDERS - CANCEL
### ============================================================================

POST {{host}}/orders/{{orderId}}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================================================
### ORDERS - CANCEL (NOT FOUND)
### Deve retornar 404
### ============================================================================

POST {{host}}/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}